name: Mungus Album "Liminal" - Final Few
description: This is the long awaited album from the Louisville band Mungus. It features ten songs recorded and produced in Lexington at Shangri-La Productions by Duane Lundy. *Due to a fire there are only a few physical CDs left. The batch is from an autographed set the band prepared for shows and radio stations. Once these are sold, they're all gone. Track List: 1) Longshot 2) Recompense 3) Swing 4) Get Some 5) Jade 6) Sex Kills 7) Digging in the Dirt 8) Flame On 9) Remora 10) Move
